  "summary": "## Summary: Cross-platform Sharing Feature\n\n### Changes Implemented\n- No changes were implemented — the required file operation tools (Bash, Read, Write, Edit, Glob, TodoWrite) are not available in this environment.\n\n### Files Modified\n- None\n\n### Notes for Developer\n- The core Claude Code CLI tools needed for file operations are missing from this session.\n- To implement this feature, the following plan should be followed once tools are available:\n  1. Add `share_plus` package to `pubspec.yaml`\n  2. Create a share service/helper that wraps the share_plus API\n  3. Add share buttons to the video list/downloaded videos UI\n  4. Include video metadata (title, description) in shared content\n  5. Handle platform-specific share behavior (iOS, Android)\n- Restart the session or verify Claude Code configuration to restore file operation tools.\n\n### Verification Status\n- Could not verify — Playwright testing requires file system access which is unavailable."
